text: Petrus "Piet" Godefridus de Brouwer (5 October 1880 - 5 October 1953) was an archer from the Netherlands. De Brouwer competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Piet de Brouwer == References == Category:1880 births Category:1953 deaths Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
